snippet.title: Unbroken - Official Action Trailer | The MIX Showcase October 2023
snippet.description: Check out the latest trailer for Unbroken to see gameplay and more from this upcoming action adventure game. Brave the hostile lands in search of your goal. Forge your own path and discover the many secrets of the realm and the looming Township of Westfall. Unlock new abilities, perks, and weapons. Soak in the atmosphere and head forth against all odds.
